uiEntry.title: skill_points
uiEntry.tooltip: Spend skill points by clicking on a skill icon, which will light up a dot to the side of it.||Some skills have more than one dot, which means more points can be spent on it, levelling it up.||If an icon is greyed out, it means you have to fulfill a requirement before it is available.||Characters earn skill points by succeeding in their specialist fields.||If you change your mind, you can click the reset skill points button, but only before you leave the panel.

uiEntry.title: button_accept
uiEntry.tooltip: Accept changes||You cannot change your selection once you click this button.||If you want to change your selection first, click the reset button.

uiEntry.title: button_cancel
uiEntry.tooltip: Cancel changes||This will close this panel. To change your selection without closing, press the reset button.

uiEntry.title: button_reset
uiEntry.tooltip: Reset||This will undo any changes you have made since opening this panel.
